summary: Adds a small Player home across from Honningbrew Meadery.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a small Lore friendly player home across from Honningbrew Meadery.
The House and area around is fully navmeshed.

Features.
Two beds
Cooking pot
Alchemy Table
Blacksmith anvil
Tanning Rack
one functional bookshelf
And most importantly...A cow.

Change Log...

V1.2
Added more Clutter and furniture.
Added a few Idle Markers for Sandboxing Followers.
Fixed Bookshelf.

V1.3
Fixed Navmesh issue outside the house.

Compatibility...
This mod is incompatible with any mod that changes the location of the house.
Such as
Provincial Courier Service.

Please report any incompatible mods in the comment section.

Recommended Mods...
Honningbrew Village http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50800/?
Tamriel Reloaded...http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/46925/?

If you use Honningbrew Village. Place this mod after it in the load order.
author: Vencent Reapers
